No. D-2508. In the Matter of Discipline of Earl D. Munroe. 562 U.S. 810, 131 S. Ct. 399,

178 L. Ed. 2d 264,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7570. October 4, 2010.

Earl D. Munroe, of Saugus, Massachusetts, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 *265days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
